de.tum.in.osgi.utility.configuration

Class NamespaceConfigurationServiceDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tum.in.osgi.utility.configuration.AbstractItemConfigurationService
      • de.tum.in.osgi.utility.configuration.NamespaceConfigurationServiceDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConfigurationService

    public class NamespaceConfigurationServiceDecorator
extends AbstractItemConfigurationService

    Title: NamespaceConfigurationServiceDecorator

    Description: Decorator for an IConfigurationService that extends all keys by a namespace. If there is no value for the extended key, the normal key will used to try to get a default value

    Author:
    AMIT KUMAR MONDAL
